title: Mr. Peanutbutter’s Hollywoo Heist
description: The amazing story of Mr. Peanutbutter stealing the D from the Hollywood sign as a surprise for his girlfriend.
quote: We bring out the best in each other. I’m the chocolate and you’re Mr. Peanutbutter!
altHero: BoJack Horseman as Mr. Peanutbutter hugs Naomi Watts as Diane
